{
  "stem": "1537.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They showed-- it's a propaganda film that show the way the Jews are cheating the Christians.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They're stealing the money from them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And in the middle of the studying, you know, in the yeshiva, they came, those, the Hungarian Hitler Jugend what they call.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They used to call it Levente in Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they jumped in through the door.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they started to chase everybody out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I jumped out of the window.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they started to beat us up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they chased us to go to see the movie.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "This is the first time I saw.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Because we were not supposed to go to see movies.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So I remembered they-- it was two kilometers they were chasing me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Some of the guys, they were able to run away.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But I was caught in the middle with another three, four, yeshiva [INAUDIBLE], what they call them.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And they chased us into the movie.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They had to watch it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And they were make-- ridicule us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And they were beating us and laughing about us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And that's where the real problem started already.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And then in [INAUDIBLE]-- of course I'm jumping back also-- when you are 12 years old, once a week, they had to take us for labor, hard labor, to-- also with the yellow star.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And they used to beat the hell out from us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And they used to make us crawl in the mud kilometers just to punish us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "That's the way every week.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "This was, it started already.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Every day, you took the newspaper, a new law came out against the Jew.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "So it was already-- we knew already something was going to happen.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "But we didn't know what concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "This, we didn't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
